00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:05,900
英文字幕：Lesson 62. After the fire.
中文字幕：课62。火灾之后。

2
00:00:06,000 --> 00:00:11,900
英文字幕：First, listen and then answer the question.
中文字幕：首先，听录音，然后回答问题。

3
00:00:12,000 --> 00:00:18,900
英文字幕：What was the danger to the villages after the fire?
中文字幕：火灾发生后，村庄面临的危险是什么？

4
00:00:19,000 --> 00:00:28,300
英文字幕：Firemen had been fighting the forest fire for nearly three weeks before they could get it under control.
中文字幕：消防员已经与森林大火搏斗了近三周，才将其控制住。

5
00:00:29,000 --> 00:00:35,900
英文字幕：A short time before, great trees had covered the countryside for miles around.
中文字幕：不久前，几英里外的乡村都长满了大树。

6
00:00:36,000 --> 00:00:43,900
英文字幕：Now, smoke still rose up from the warm ground over the death of the hills.
中文字幕：现在，烟雾仍然从温暖的地面升起，笼罩着山丘的死亡。

7
00:00:44,000 --> 00:00:50,900
英文字幕：Winter was coming on, and the hills threatened the surrounding villages with destruction.
中文字幕：冬天来了，群山威胁着周围的村庄。

8
00:00:51,000 --> 00:00:58,900
英文字幕：For heavy rain would not only wash away the soil, but would cause serious floods as well.
中文字幕：因为大雨不仅会冲走土壤，还会造成严重的洪水。

9
00:00:59,000 --> 00:01:10,900
英文字幕：When the fire had at last been put out, the forest authorities ordered several tons of a special type of grass seed which would grow quickly.
中文字幕：当大火终于被扑灭时，林业部门订购了几吨一种生长迅速的特殊草籽。

10
00:01:11,000 --> 00:01:18,900
英文字幕：The seed was sprayed over the ground in huge quantities by aeroplanes.
中文字幕：飞机把种子大量地撒在地上。

11
00:01:19,000 --> 00:01:24,900
英文字幕：The plains had been planting seed for nearly a month when it began to rain.
中文字幕：平原上播种已经快一个月了，这时开始下雨了。

12
00:01:25,000 --> 00:01:30,900
英文字幕：By then, however, in many places the grass had already taken root.
中文字幕：然而，到那时，在许多地方，草已经扎根了。

13
00:01:31,000 --> 00:01:42,300
英文字幕：In place of the great trees which had been growing there for centuries, patches of green had begun to appear in the blackened soil.
中文字幕：取而代之的是几个世纪以来一直生长在那里的大树，在变黑的土壤中开始出现一片片绿色。

14
00:01:50,000 --> 00:01:57,900
英文字幕：The forest was planted in the forest for nearly a month, and the forest was planted in the forest for nearly a month.
中文字幕：这片森林在森林里种了将近一个月，这片森林也在森林里种植了近一个月。

